{"type": "article", "id": 6382, "title": "伦敦路人的变装秀", "description": null, "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": null, "column": null, "author": 8, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/default_images/missing_article.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#1F0909;font-family:'PT Serif';line-height:24px;white-space:normal;\">摄影师汤姆·强森（Tom Johnson）和造型师菲比·海涅斯（Phoebe Haines）在伦敦街头随便抓了一些路人，给后者搭配他们觉得最合适的衣服。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#1F0909;font-family:'PT Serif';line-height:24px;white-space:normal;\">当一个路人从原本通勤的衣着中换成这一身戏剧感十足的衣服，气质也就瞬间变了。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#1F0909;font-family:'PT Serif';line-height:24px;white-space:normal;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060421385825Y1glTVKCXsvM9t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.16666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604213859S5hPicRbWzeagJo1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.16666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606042138597GPOZ8cNsHV1SFz6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.16666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604213859ju0t7JdSnPOvNUrH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.16666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604213900A0pNTuahb6VfYxni.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.16666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604213901RtIkM2AmXvsxTCQL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.16666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606042139022KJheCLOg3ZtBsIR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.16666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604213902ujB6XHOTKh9ctkmf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.16666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604213903920K6ugLNmPFZjw3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.16666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#1F0909;font-family:'PT Serif';line-height:24px;white-space:normal;\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}